---
<BaseLayout
  title="Dental Practice Website Design Maryland | Upcoming Brand"
  description="WordPress website design for Maryland dental practices. Dentist schema, online booking, 90+ PageSpeed. Fixed-scope from $1,500. Baltimore, Annapolis, Frederick."
  canonicalUrl="https://upcomingbrand.com/industries/dental-website-design/"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} slot="head" />

  <Navigation />

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="lfh-hero">

    <div class="container">
      <nav class="lfh-breadcrumb mono-xs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <a href="/#industries">Industries</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <span>Dental Website Design</span>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="container lfh-wrap">

      <!-- LEFT COLUMN -->
      <div class="lfh-left">

        <div class="lfh-tags">
          <span class="lfh-pill">
            <span class="lfh-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            Dental Practice Web Design &middot; Maryland
          </span>
          <span class="lfh-hero-sep" aria-hidden="true">&#183;</span>
          <span class="lfh-hero-eyebrow">A specialist studio, not a template shop</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="lfh-h1">
          <span class="lfh-h1-line">Maryland dental websites</span>
          <span class="lfh-h1-line lfh-h1-accent-line"><em class="lfh-h1-accent">built to fill chairs</em></span>
          <span class="lfh-h1-line lfh-h1-italic">and grow practices.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="lfh-lede">
          Most dental practice websites lose patients before the first call: slow load times, no Dentist schema, and booking forms that break on mobile. We build WordPress sites for Maryland dentists that rank in the Local Pack, load fast, and turn visitors into booked appointments. Fixed-scope from <strong>$1,500</strong>.
        </p>

        <div class="lfh-ctas">
          <a href="#contact" class="lfh-btn-primary">
            Book a discovery call
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M1 7h12M8 2l5 5-5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#pricing" class="lfh-btn-ghost">
            See pricing
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M2 12L12 2M12 2H5M12 2v7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="lfh-trust">
          <span class="lfh-trust-item">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="5.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-opacity="0.35"/><path d="M3.5 6l2 2 3-3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Maryland-based studio
          </span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-item">Dentist schema on every build</span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-item">Fixed-scope pricing &middot; no surprises</span>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT COLUMN - FORM -->
      <div class="lfh-right">
        <div class="lfh-form-card">
          <div class="lfh-form-header">
            <p class="lfh-form-eyebrow">Free site audit</p>
            <h2 class="lfh-form-title">Is your website losing you patients?</h2>
            <p class="lfh-form-sub">We review your current site and send a plain-English audit within 2 business days. No sales call required.</p>
          </div>

          <form class="lfh-form" name="dental-inquiry"-honeypot="bot-field" data-uc-form="dental-inquiry" method="POST" novalidate>
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="dental-inquiry" />
            <div style="position:absolute;left:-9999px;width:1px;height:1px;overflow:hidden;" aria-hidden="true">
              <label>Leave blank: <input type="text" name="bot-field" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" /></label>
            </div>

            <div class="lfh-form-row">
              <label class="lfh-form-label" for="d-name">Your name</label>
              <input class="lfh-form-input" type="text" id="d-name" name="name" placeholder="Dr. Rachel Okonkwo" required autocomplete="name" />
            </div>

            <div class="lfh-form-row">
              <label class="lfh-form-label" for="d-email">Email address</label>
              <input class="lfh-form-input" type="email" id="d-email" name="email" placeholder="dr.okonkwo@dental.com" required autocomplete="email" />
            </div>

            <div class="lfh-form-row">
              <label class="lfh-form-label" for="d-practice">Practice name</label>
              <input class="lfh-form-input" type="text" id="d-practice" name="practice" placeholder="Chesapeake Family Dental" autocomplete="organization" />
            </div>

            <div class="lfh-form-row">
